<br>
The songs fades as it lands was brought up as you said, along with a couple of other sync issues.  After what I heard both in summit and at faire dont expect this fixed.  It sounds like its more of a web issue then a game issue.  As in, the time it takes for the server to receive the information that you started your song.  So if we all played in San Diego attached to SOE's servers, this wouldnt exist.  They are working on it, but this is a very difficult process since they cant just make all those calculations server-side.  And to be blunt, I do not intend to have this even be an option on the new poll.  I dont feel that it taking up space on our top 10 is worthwhile since I have been assured it is being worked on, but is an almost impossible fix.  And its not just us it effects, nor is it just spells.<br>
<br>
FoF-crap, I forgot to ask about that.  I'll look into it.<br>
<br>
Puretone-Didnt I bring that up?  I honestly dont remember.  However, disciplines for hybrids were brought up a few times.  Let me check my notes and figure out what they said.<br>
